00:38:30,720 --> 00:38:33,180
 Želim poručiti majkama da nisu same,

544
00:38:33,180 --> 00:38:35,360
 da ih Bog vidi,

545
00:38:35,360 --> 00:38:38,540
 da Bog uživa u onome što ne rade

546
00:38:38,540 --> 00:38:41,240
 i da su dragocijene,

547
00:38:41,240 --> 00:38:46,120
 da će vidjeti plodove uživati u plodovima svog služenja.

548
00:38:46,120 --> 00:38:50,280
 Evo, Marina, i za kraj ispičat ćeš nam čime se baviš.

549
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:52,060
 Što si nam ovo donesla?

550
00:38:53,340 --> 00:38:55,860
 Ovako, dugi niz godina se bavimo pčelarstvom.

551
00:38:55,860 --> 00:39:01,020
 Suprugova želja da imamo svoj med.

552
00:39:01,020 --> 00:39:02,460
 Baš fino miriši.

553
00:39:05,660 --> 00:39:08,360
 Kroz pčelarstvo se izrodila ideja

554
00:39:08,360 --> 00:39:09,740
 da radimo ljekovite kreme,

555
00:39:09,740 --> 00:39:11,380
 znači balzame i

556
00:39:11,380 --> 00:39:13,780
 evo ovo sad što držiš u rukama je

557
00:39:13,780 --> 00:39:14,900
 balzam za usne,

558
00:39:14,900 --> 00:39:16,180
 prirodnje labelo,

559
00:39:16,180 --> 00:39:19,860
 na bazi ulja i čistog pčelinjeg voska.

560
00:39:19,860 --> 00:39:22,040
 Vosa koji koristimo,

561
00:39:22,040 --> 00:39:23,860
 to je nekako jedna moja ljubav.

562
00:39:25,860 --> 00:39:27,920
 pored djece da mogu nešto raditi za sebe,

563
00:39:27,920 --> 00:39:30,820
 neka kreativa kojim je Bog dao tu kreativnost

564
00:39:30,820 --> 00:39:35,180
 i spojila sam jednostavno u te ljekovite proizvode.

565
00:39:35,180 --> 00:39:37,920
 Koristimo najkvalitetniji pčelinji vosak,

566
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:39,080
 to je zapravo od poklopaca,

567
00:39:39,080 --> 00:39:39,860
 njega nema puno.

568
00:39:39,860 --> 00:39:42,220
 Znači najbolji vosak

569
00:39:42,220 --> 00:39:44,640
 koji se skida kapica po kapica

570
00:39:44,640 --> 00:39:47,200
 i to se mora par puta otopiti,

571
00:39:47,200 --> 00:39:48,800
 pretopiti, procijediti

572
00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:51,940
 i onda nastaju ti proizvodi.

573
00:39:51,940 --> 00:39:54,960
 Radimo ljekovite balzame,

574
00:39:55,100 --> 00:39:56,520
 znači gavez, stolisnik,

575
00:39:56,520 --> 00:39:57,940
 djećju kremu,

576
00:39:57,940 --> 00:39:59,660
 kremu za njegu lice i tijela.

577
00:39:59,660 --> 00:40:03,180
 Dobro, a vi ćete imati priliku

578
00:40:03,180 --> 00:40:06,080
 osvojiti jedan proizvod od Marine.

579
00:40:06,080 --> 00:40:08,180
 Marina, reci mi,

580
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:10,360
 gdje te trebaju na Facebooku zapratiti?

581
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:11,900
 Kako se zove Facebook stranica?

582
00:40:11,900 --> 00:40:13,600
 Facebook stranica je

583
00:40:13,600 --> 00:40:15,300
 OPG Pčelarstvo Rokić.

584
00:40:15,300 --> 00:40:17,600
 Dobro, mi ćemo vam sve napisati

585
00:40:17,600 --> 00:40:18,520
 što trebate napraviti.

586
00:40:18,520 --> 00:40:19,920
 I još mi za kraj reci,

587
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:21,000
 naime ti muž,

588
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:22,640
 imate još zajedničko poslanje,

589
00:40:22,640 --> 00:40:24,780
 radite sa parovima, je li tako?

590
00:40:24,840 --> 00:40:27,200
 Suprug i ja radimo sa bračnim parovima,

591
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:28,780
 radimo radionice,

592
00:40:28,780 --> 00:40:30,380
 umijeće bračnog odnosa.

593
00:40:30,380 --> 00:40:33,640
 Kroz te radionice upoznajemo sebe,

594
00:40:33,640 --> 00:40:35,800
 upoznajemo kako funkcioniramo.

595
00:40:35,800 --> 00:40:38,280
 Svaki par za sebe ima svoju dinamiku.

596
00:40:38,280 --> 00:40:42,120
 Kako zajedno plesati ovaj ples do starosti?

597
00:40:42,800 --> 00:40:44,600
 Predivno, kako vam se mogu javiti?

598
00:40:44,600 --> 00:40:47,060
 Suprug i ja vodimo jednu kršćansku zajednicu

599
00:40:47,060 --> 00:40:48,420
 kao se zove Put istine.

600
00:40:48,420 --> 00:40:51,140
 Nalazimo se u Svesesom Hraljecu

601
00:40:51,140 --> 00:40:53,760
 i vodimo, znači, bračne parove,

602
00:40:53,760 --> 00:40:55,300
 omladinske susrete,

603
00:40:55,300 --> 00:40:56,780
 susrete mladih.

604
00:40:56,780 --> 00:40:58,360
 Ja vodim

605
00:40:58,360 --> 00:40:59,980
 sastanak žena.

606
00:40:59,980 --> 00:41:03,180
 Kako rasti, razvijati i otkriti svrhu svog poziva?

607
00:41:05,060 --> 00:41:05,580
 Odlično.

608
00:41:05,580 --> 00:41:07,640
 Onda se sigurno vidimo i na osnaženoj.

609
00:41:07,640 --> 00:41:13,940
 Evo, Marina, hvala ti puno, preživjela si.

610
00:41:13,940 --> 00:41:15,760
 Marina, imamo i mi za tebe poklon,

611
00:41:15,760 --> 00:41:17,080
 ne samo da si ti nama donijela,

612
00:41:17,080 --> 00:41:17,860
 nego i mi tebe.

613
00:41:17,860 --> 00:41:19,400
 Evo, jedan mali znak pažnje

614
00:41:19,400 --> 00:41:22,820
 što si sudjelovala i bila odvažna u osnaženoj.

615
00:41:22,820 --> 00:41:24,140
 Hvala ti puno.

616
00:41:24,140 --> 00:41:26,780
 Hvala ti Marijeta, hvala ti na pozivu.

617
00:41:26,780 --> 00:41:27,140
 Molim.

618
00:41:27,140 --> 00:41:29,960
 A vas sve, naravno, potičemo

619
00:41:29,960 --> 00:41:32,620
 da ovaj video šerate svim ženama i majkama

620
00:41:32,620 --> 00:41:33,640
 koje trebaju ovo čuti.

621
00:41:34,440 --> 00:41:36,140
 zapratite Marinu na Facebook stanci.

622
00:41:36,140 --> 00:41:38,240
 Mi ćemo sve detaljno ispod napisati

623
00:41:38,240 --> 00:41:40,240
 što trebate učiniti.

624
00:41:40,240 --> 00:41:42,160
 I vidimo se u sljedećem podcastu.

625
00:41:42,160 --> 00:41:43,080
 Pozdrav!

626
00:41:43,080 --> 00:41:43,740
 Pozdrav!

